tags: [[Running Conversion]]
title: Convert Button
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

''Convert'' runs the engine on the current source + profile.  No wiki tiddlers are written; everything lands in a sandbox under `$:/temp/json-convert/staged/...`.  The Convert button is enabled as soon as there's both source text and a selected profile.

Clicking ''Convert'' a second time replaces the previous run's output -- there's no "append" mode.  If you want to keep yesterday's staged batch, ''Apply'' or ''Cancel'' it before running the next conversion.
